roadmap SH-OMEGA active "terminal: zero external C-compiler on AOT path (partial: residual audit verified file-wide, W-α/W-α' shape spec done; smoke-build-blocking residual = 2, both wedges 1-line copy-paste pending rebuild window)"
  omega-stop fixpoint-convergence

